2012 Bexar Bench Motions Trials Supporting tagline

This presentation was given at the Bexar County Bench Motions and Trials continuing legal education seminar in May 2012.  Presenters are Judge Richard Price, Judge Cathy Stryker, and attorney Nathan Roach.  The presentation follows updates on the topic of e-discovery of Electronically Stored Information.
